---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lang = 'en';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us | Kinarray"
  description="Shanghai Feixiong Electronic Technology Co. LTD, founded in 2018, focuses on micro-deformation and micro-vibration radar for slope and infrastructure health monitoring."
  lang={lang}
>
  <main class="bg-slate-50">
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-900 py-24">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#334155_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#334155_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:4rem_4rem] opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="absolute -top-20 left-1/4 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-blue-600/20 blur-[100px]"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-16 right-1/4 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-orange-500/10 blur-[100px]"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-blue-300">About Us</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-white md:text-5xl">
          Kinarray and Feixiong Electronic Technology
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
          Founded in 2018, Shanghai Feixiong Electronic Technology Co. LTD focuses on R&D and production of micro-deformation and micro-vibration radar.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-8 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:px-8">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Who We Are</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
            Our products are widely used in risk-slope monitoring and health monitoring of large man-made structures across multiple industries.
            Kinarray is the core brand for our highway slope radar solutions.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Technical Strength</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
            Our team includes experts from globally leading radar and geoscience institutions, with fully independent intellectual property.
            For highway slope scenarios, we developed mid-range and long-range deformation radar models such as S500 and S1000.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-slate-100 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 md:p-10 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 md:text-3xl">Product Advantages and Commitment</h2>
          <p class="mt-5 leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
            Our products provide large-area coverage, high precision, low power consumption, no targets required, and no on-site tuning.
            They are highly recognized by users in real projects.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
            We stay committed to technology innovation, quality assurance, and integrity. We value the long-term interests of users and partners, and seek like-minded, influential partners for deep collaboration to build an industry benchmark and a true safety shield for slope monitoring.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
